metadata.name: Hannya - Ochite Kuru Sakura
metadata.description:
This 1/1 NFT is the 1st MINT of my Foundation Journey. 

Hannya - Ochite Kuru Sakura

Ochite Kuru Sakura directly translates to "falling cherry blossoms." 

After creating the mask and background on procreate, I decided to contrast the dark image with bright colors and cherry blossoms. The falling pedals add a nice flow and a feeling of serenity to balance the demonic beauty of the Hannya Mask.

This is #001. Thank you for looking.
